description:
Begin SharePoint programming while learning to integrate Google Maps & Garmin GPS with SharePoint in less than 2hrs! With this Sharepoint Programming Tutorial.

This SharePoint Quick Start is a one of a series of unique courses designed to walk you through the development of creative solutions for the SharePoint 2010/2013 platform.

You will learn Photo Geotagging by building SharePoint Extensions to process Geo-tagged photos, interface with Garmin GPS and integrate with Google Maps.
title: SharePoint Quick Starts: Building GeoPhoto Mapping Websites
